      About this item

      • PRACTICAL AND PORTABLE: Foldies adjust to your lifestyle, making it so simple to collapse and store your sunglasses without compromising comfort or quality. Our compact design allows you to take your shades anywhere without carrying a bulky case. Just throw them in your bag and head out.
      • TIMELESS DESIGN: Yes, they fold! But they are also stylish and comfortable so you can look your best at the beach, the pool, or the golf course. With our classic always-in-style design, we're sure you'll find a new pair of sunglasses you can love.
      • PREMIUM CONSTRUCTION: Engineered to be reliable and made using only high-grade materials, you can look good and know your glasses will endure everyday use and stand the test of time. Don't sacrifice quality for price; we design premium and high-end sunglasses at an affordable price. All our folding sunglasses come with scratch-resistant lenses and a two-year warranty.
      • 100% POLARIZED PROTECTION: Our proprietary 7-Layer HepTEK Polarized Lenses offer 100% full-spectrum UV protection, including UVA, UVB, and UV400. The combination of polarization and 100% UV protection allows for better and brighter vision without eyestrain.
      • LEATHER CARRYING CASE & MICROFIBER CLEANING CLOTH: Our custom case is built with durable vegan leather and a soft velvet interior to protect your Foldies. The premium cleaning cloth is guaranteed to safely remove fingerprints, dust, and watermarks from your polarized sunglasses. Best of all, it's compact and hassle-free.

          Foldies Aviators

All of our polarized Aviators have our proprietary HepTEK 7-layer lens system and are available in various mirrored and classic lenses.

                  How customer reviews and ratings work

                  Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

                  To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

                  I recently purchased the round Foldies sunglasses in classic brown and gold after falling in love with them in-store. I had been wanting a round pair of glasses and these seemed to be the perfect size, and they really are a perfect fit. These glasses provide comfort, durability, 100% sun-blocking, easy storage, and are very lightweight. If you're a girl who struggles with carrying too much with not enough space, then you know what I mean!! On top of all the functionality these sunglasses offer, they are so stylish and trendy!                   3.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful Lenses but not as Functional as I thought...
                  Reviewed in the United States on September 5, 2018
                  Color: Gold - Pink MirrorLens Width: 58 MillimetersVerified Purchase
                  I have had these sunnies for almost 2 months now and I have mixed feelings. I REALLY like the color of the lens and frames. The pink is beautiful and I get tons of compliments! They are nicely compact which fit well in a small cross body bag for outings.

                  The downside(s): the folding hinge right on the temple scratches the inside of the lens when I go to put them away. I have to wrap the lens with the cleaning cloth before I fold them to put them in their case. The other issue was that the nose pad popped off on one side after using them only 7-10 times and I still can't get it back on the pad arm correctly. Lastly, the hinges have becomes really loose over the short period of time that I have used them. When I want to take the off and set them down on my desk or counter, they fold up and it causes the lenses to hit the counter. I haven't scratched them ye, but this is a two handed job to set them down without them folding in and falling forward.

                  If I could do over, I would probably have spent the additional money on RayBans.
